data.description: Welcome home to this renovated beauty in Dale City that you will just fall in love with! Move right in to this 2,200+ finished square foot home that boasts four bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, a one car garage, and has been renovated top to bottom. In 2022, NEW 50 year roof with architectural shingles, siding, front porch, sidewalk, driveway. In 2021, NEW Pergo waterproof flooring on the main level. Some other recent improvements include: 18ft round above-ground pool in 2017, windows and 6 foot privacy fence in 2016, HVAC in 2015, and water heater in 2012. There are new light fixtures and finishes throughout the home. As you enter through the front double doors, you are greeted by the bright living room with its elegant trim, chair railing, ceiling fan, and casement windows. The nearby dining room continues the elegance with its trim work and chair railing but also includes a modern chandelier, and a picturesque front window. The dining room opens to the kitchen and the chef of the home will enjoy cooking here! Stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, plenty of cabinets, tile flooring, backsplash, and french doors that lead to the tiered deck. There are three bedrooms on the main level all with ceiling fans and ample closet space. The primary bathroom and the hall full bathroom have been renovated as well. Step on down to the fully finished basement. Here you will find the huge rec room, the fourth bedroom, half bathroom, and laundry room. Walkout in the fenced-in backyard from here for added convenience. The homeowners have enjoyed having a huge backyard to include swimming in their above-ground pool and letting their pets have tons of room to run and play. The homeowners will miss the quietness and friendliness of the neighborhood. No HOA and ready for you! Hurry, you don't want to miss this one!
